OL,3,CFormer Radio One DJ Tim Westwood to
OL,4,Cappear in court again in December
OL,6,FFormer BBC Radio One DJ Tim Westwood,
OL,7,Fwho denies multiple sex offences
OL,8,Fincluding rape and sexual assault,
OL,9,Fwill next appear in court in December.
OL,11,FThe 68-year-old is accused of sex
OL,12,Foffences against seven women dating
OL,13,Fback to 1983, including three indecent
OL,14,Fassaults at the BBC studios in the
OL,15,F1990s.
OL,17,FThe former Capital Xtra DJ was excused
OL,18,Ffrom attending a further case
OL,19,Fmanagement hearing at Southwark Crown
OL,20,FCourt on Monday.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
