OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1775127596
OL,3,CFormer Radio One DJ Tim Westwood to
OL,4,Cappear in court again in December
OL,6,FThe hearing was set to facilitate
OL,7,Fdisclosure between the prosecution and
OL,8,FWestwood's defence team.
OL,10,FHis trial is set to begin on January
OL,11,F25 next year, and Westwood will next
OL,12,Fappear at a pre-trial review on
OL,13,FDecember 14.
OL,15,FWestwood is accused of four indecent
OL,16,Fassaults in the 1980s in London, as
OL,17,Fwell as the three indecent assaults at
OL,18,Fthe BBC in the 1990s.
OL,20,FThe defendant is also alleged to have
OL,21,Fraped a woman in a hotel in 1996.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
