PN,40803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1775127596
OL,3,CFormer Radio One DJ Tim Westwood to
OL,4,Cappear in court again in December
OL,6,FWestwood is further accused of two
OL,7,Findecent assaults and one count of
OL,8,Frape from the early 2000s at a London
OL,9,Faddress, and two counts of rape at a
OL,10,FLondon address in the 2010s.
OL,12,FHe is also alleged to have sexually
OL,13,Fassaulted a woman at a nightclub in
OL,14,FStroud, Gloucestershire, in 2010.
OL,16,FWestwood, who has been granted bail on
OL,17,Fthe condition he does not contact the
OL,18,Fcomplainants, has pleaded not guilty
OL,19,Fto all charges.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/4
